{"tid":1294272,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【引渡惡法】警方唔克制驅散示威者：認X住我呀！隻揪呀！","createTime":"2019-07-07T18:08:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T18:24:09.000Z","uid":16792,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0df3ae779a9bf59cabaf6bb5d7268205623bdc74","tid":1294272,"uid":16792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T18:08:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190708/59799355\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190708%2F59799355&d=Tc8prIKBo9hF1z3tnQ%2BJRi3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=b569ea7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190708%2F59799355&h=d31cee8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190708/59799355</a><br />\n<br />\n警方晚上於旺角彌敦道驅散示威者，其中有一條片段在telegram群組流傳，清楚見到有警員驅散示威者期間，一名年約20歲的男子絆倒在地上，在場示威人士不齒警方強硬驅散，於是破口大罵，但警員竟然沒有克制，大聲呼喝：「咩呀！」，之後雙方不斷推撞，有警員更指：「認X住我呀」「隻揪呀」，意圖令示威者的不滿情緒加劇。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>佢話認撚住佢喎，不如一齊嚟認下佢究竟係邊個？</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"d670744c5d64376e8a6d601ca2c8a8bf73e684b2","tid":1294272,"uid":107574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T18:24:09.000Z","msg":"係咪又要表揚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}